<div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center  mb-3 mb-md-5 dynamic-content">
    <div class="col-md-6 h-100">
        <h2 class="display-1 fw-bold mb-3">unTill Prime – made just for you</h2>
        <div class="introtext-rich-bullets-primary">
            <p>unTill Prime is made for businesses that need flexibility, advanced features, and a setup that adapts fully to their workflow. Ideal for big restaurants, hotels, and ambitious entrepreneurs who want top-level service.</p>
<ul>
<li>Customise everything, compromise nothing.</li>
<li>125+ integrations with leading hospitality software.</li>
<li>Packed with premium features to flex with you.</li>
<li>Outstanding service from our certified resellers at all times.</li>
</ul>
<p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-xs" href="prime" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discover unTill Prime</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center mb-5 mb-md-0 gx-3">
        
        <img src="/assets/components/phpthumbof/cache/header-13.a49ab6c320da62e5b1e84cdc97270833.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Home">
        
    </div>
    
</div>

<div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center flex-md-row-reverse mb-3 mb-md-5 dynamic-content">
    <div class="col-md-6 h-100">
        <h2 class="display-1 fw-bold mb-3">unTill Air – Simple. Smart. Efficient.</h2>
        <div class="introtext-rich-bullets-primary">
            <p>unTill Air is a perfect match for smaller businesses who value simplicity, speed, and affordability. An excellent choice for small caf&eacute;s and bars, food trucks and any pop-up concepts ready to move fast without compromising quality.</p>
<ul>
<li>Easy-to-use to use POS with all the essentials included.</li>
<li>Cloud-based and super mobile.</li>
<li>A fully professional POS app &mdash; from just &euro;19.</li>
<li>Flexible hardware. Quick onboarding.</li>
</ul>
<p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-xs" href="untill-air" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discover unTill Air</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center mb-5 mb-md-0 gx-3">
        
        <img src="/assets/components/phpthumbof/cache/header2.a49ab6c320da62e5b1e84cdc97270833.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Home">
        
    </div>
    
</div>

<div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center  mb-3 mb-md-5 dynamic-content">
    <div class="col-md-6 h-100">
        <h2 class="display-1 fw-bold mb-3">unTill Payments brings it all together</h2>
        <div class="introtext-rich-bullets-primary">
            <p data-start="183" data-end="388">unTill Payments is a modern, secure payment system developed by unTill &mdash; so you can accept payments seamlessly and instantly, right from your POS. All-in-one solution? Exactly. That&rsquo;s what it is.</p>
<p data-start="390" data-end="544">It&rsquo;s built into both unTill Prime and unTill Air, so no matter which system you use, you&rsquo;ll benefit from fully integrated payments that just work.</p>
<ul>
<li>Mobile, scalable, and cost-effective.</li>
<li>Accept all modern payment methods.</li>
<li>Regular and accurate payouts. No surprises.</li>
<li>Quick and smooth setup.</li>
<li>Use your phone as a payment device or go with a fixed terminal? It&rsquo;s up to you!</li>
</ul>
<p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-xs" href="untill-payments" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discover unTill Payments</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center mb-5 mb-md-0 gx-3">
        
        <img src="/assets/components/phpthumbof/cache/payments-tap-to-pay.a49ab6c320da62e5b1e84cdc97270833.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Home">
        
    </div>
    
</div>

<div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center flex-md-row-reverse mb-3 mb-md-5 dynamic-content">
    <div class="col-md-6 h-100">
        <h2 class="display-1 fw-bold mb-3">unTill WebManagement</h2>
        <div class="introtext-rich-bullets-primary">
            <p>Stay in control of your business &mdash; anytime, anywhere.</p>
<p>With unTill WebManagement, you can access your unTill Prime system 24/7 through the cloud. Track performance, manage products and pricing, monitor your team, and generate powerful reports &mdash; all from one intuitive platform.</p>
<p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-xs" href="untill-webmanagement" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discover unTill WebManagement</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center mb-5 mb-md-0 gx-3">
        
        <img src="/assets/components/phpthumbof/cache/webmanagement.f8aea764ba3bbd1c52bf928d0e0fd9d3.png" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Home">
        
